data.description: A very nice 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in a great spot for schools, shopping & access to Highway 101.  It has good bones, newer windows & is ready for you to add your decorating touches.  The living area has large windows looking out onto the big yard & also features a propane stove on a brick hearth. The dining room opens to a large covered deck that is perfect for rainy bar-b-ques.  The primary bedroom has a full bath & the other two bedrooms are nice sized.  Covered parking for 3 vehicles & there is a shed & greenhouse as well.  Most of the 1/3 acre corner lot is fenced & provides good privacy.  A perfect spot to start out or to size down!  Includes a kitchen full of appliances too! Gig speed Internet - perfect for a home office.
